                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n\t\t\t\t<addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(2)\">Esteemed Friend</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(4)\">Enclosed please<lb/> find a check on the Philadelphia Bank,<lb/> for\n\t\t\t\tsix hundred dollars as a loan for a indefin<lb/>ite period, from a few friends, who\n\t\t\t\thave<lb/> learned with deep regret of the loss of your<lb/> valuable books by\n\t\t\t\tfire–<lb/> I sincerely trust that you will soon be<lb/> able to reproduce other\n\t\t\t\teditions of those<lb/> excellent works that ought and I have no<lb/> doubt will,\n\t\t\t\tfind their way into the families<lb/> of all Israelites–</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(2)\">With the highest feelings of<lb/> regard and esteem for you, I am Dr\n\t\t\t\tSir</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(9)\">Yours Sincerely</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n\t\t\t\t<persName role=\"author\">David H Solis</persName>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p>board of <persName>Mr. S. L. Florance</persName> 1,000</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\" \" \" <persName>S. Neuhouse</persName> “</p>\n\t\t\t<p>' ' ' <persName>B. Lelar</persName> “</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\" \" \" <persName>Laz. Mayer</persName> “</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\" \" <persName>Danl. Gans</persName> “</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\" \" <persName>D Hof</persName> “</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n\t\t\t\t<placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n\t\t\t\t<date>March 11<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1837</date>\n\t\t\t</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39z9123m/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
